      <title>德意志银行完成 10 亿美元 CRE 贷款组合出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/deutsche-bank-completes-sale-of-1-billion-cre-loan-portfolio</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行已完成对近 10 亿美元与美国商业房地产相关的贷款的处置，从而减少了对该业务造成压力的资产类别的风险敞口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/deutsche-bank-completes-sale-of-1-billion-cre-loan-portfolio</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 13:39:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银在瑞士信贷洗钱刑事案件中被判无罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/ubs-acquitted-over-credit-suisse-criminal-money-laundering-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士信贷因未能阻止可卡因交易商利润洗钱而被定罪，该判决在其一名前雇员因该案被判有罪死亡后于 2022 年被瑞士上诉法院推翻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/ubs-acquitted-over-credit-suisse-criminal-money-laundering-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 13:22:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
