    <item>
      <title>阿拉比卡咖啡价格飙升至 1977 年以来最高水平，咖啡价格进一步上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/coffee-gets-even-pricier-as-futures-rally-to-highest-since-1977</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受全球供应担忧影响，咖啡期货在纽约延续大幅上涨势头，升至 40 多年来的最高水平，有可能进一步提高消费者的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/coffee-gets-even-pricier-as-futures-rally-to-highest-since-1977</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:42:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC 的困境：又一年的供应限制或油价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/opec-s-dilemma-another-year-of-oil-supply-curbs-or-price-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当 OPEC+ 部长本周末开会时，他们将面临一个难以接受的选择：继续限制石油供应直至 2025 年，否则将面临油价再度暴跌的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/opec-s-dilemma-another-year-of-oil-supply-curbs-or-price-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 09:17:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>干旱导致作物减产，南非计划申请美国玉米进口许可证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/south-africa-plans-us-corn-import-permits-as-drought-cuts-crop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非将发放从美国进口的转基因白玉米和黄玉米的进口许可证，此前南非遭遇夏季干旱，导致当地玉米产量下降 23%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/south-africa-plans-us-corn-import-permits-as-drought-cuts-crop</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 08:02:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易商等待 OPEC+ 生产计划线索，油价小幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-27</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明 OPEC+ 将再次推迟恢复产量，抵消了中东地缘政治风险的缓解，油价小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-27</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 23:36:00 GMT</pubDate>
